				<li class="cd-faq-title"><h2>Basics</h2></li>
				<li>How do I change my
						password?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>On the Login/Sign Up page there is a link that states "
							forgot my password ". If you follow the link you will recieve an
							email that will allow you to reset your password.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>How do I sign up?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>Utilizing the side menu navigate to login page. The second
							tab states Sign Up, simply select the Sign Up tab and fill out
							the required information</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>Can I remove a
						post?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>As for now posts can only be managed by our Administrators.
							If you would like a post removed please contact them via the
							portal on the bottom of the page.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>How do reviews
						work?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>The review system only grants access to registered student
							that are currently attending a class that the professor is
							teaching. A registered student can rate the professor as well as
							the tutor assigned to the class. A student is only allowed one
							review in order to keep a more accurate statistics.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>
			</ul>

			<!-- cd-faq-group -->

			<ul id="account" class="cd-faq-group">
				<li class="cd-faq-title"><h2>Account</h2></li>
				<li>How do I change my
						password?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>>On the Login/Sign Up page there is a link that states "
							forgot my password ". If you follow the link you will recieve an
							email that will allow you to reset your password.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>How do I delete my
						account?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>Utilizing the side menu, while logged in you can select the
							deactivate account link. There you will have verify your email
							and password in order to deactivate the account.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>How do I change my
						account settings?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>The user would be able to manage their own profile settings
							via the user dashboard or by contacting the site admin.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>I forgot my
						password. How do I reset it?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>There are two options, option number one is to follow the
							change password link on the login page, option number two is to
							request a password recovery.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>
			</ul>
			<!-- cd-faq-group -->



