				<li>Are the accounts
						secure?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>The site account are secured via password and URL
							encryptions. This allows for us to limit the users as well as
							avoid spam and other security threats.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>Can the professor
						tell who left the review?
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>The reviews are all anonymous to the professor. Unless the
							student makes any self identifying remarks the professor would
							not know which one of his students had left the review and or
							commentary.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li>How can I access my
						account data?
